See `AGENTS.md` at the repo root for the full guide.

Key rules:
- Primitives in `packages/ui/src/components/primitives/` must re-export from `../ui/` — never from `@radix-ui/*`
- Never add CVA variants or rebuild logic in a primitive — wrap the shadcn ui/ component
- After any change to ui/ or primitives/, run `npm run sync` to push to viana-kit
- Adding a component: ui/ → primitive → index.ts → docs preview → docs page → sidebar

Full instructions → `AGENTS.md`
